commit.message:
Make memes update every 30 seconds

Memes are now taken from the /media directory, where they are generated
in parallel from another http request.
Add quotes feature for various jokes and messages
Add date and fixed image sizing
Format time to have am and pm

Refactor file system for web server support

Move all backend to cgi-bin, add initial index.html.
Web server should be run with python3 -m http.server --cgi 8000
Change UI layout to frame layout

UI Update

The UI is now a class and in main we create an instance of it.

UI Update

Add meme support for the UI and format it correctly.

UI Updates

Add updates to ui.py. The ui now uses frames to resolve the layout. Displays
current temperature in Ann Arbor in a formatted way.

Add reddit bot meme browser

Also add .gitignore

Add basic weather.py and ui.py

weather.py creates weatherData instances to be used in ui.py. ui.py creates
a window that displays the current temperature in Ann Arbor.
